  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Rapid Assistance Program for Internally Displaced: R.A.P.I.D Fund for Eastern DRC</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Through this project, IOM aims to scale up humanitarian assistance provided to conflict-affected populations in spontaneous displacement sites and surrounding communities in Eastern Democratic Republic of Congo. Within the humanitarian coordination sector, IOM will continue tosupport /set-up displacement site coordination mechanisms in targeted provinces. In the Shelter and Settlements sector, this action will be oriented towards providing targeted and context-specific emergency shelter assistance to a total of 4,000 Internally Displaced Persons (IDP) households in three provinces.</narrative>
  </description>
